{
  "stem": "11744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other one was to get somebody in a police station to sneak out the cards and the stamps and everything and-- and be on our side while working for Vichy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is the way I was able to get my husband out the third time he was taken.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that third time I was very, very anxious, because when two Germans had a fight, a brawl, in a bar a few days before, and the first thing they did was to take the prisoner who were in the last basement in the prison.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How do you call that when they had no communication with anybody?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the people they took as hostage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the minute there was something like this happening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I was terribly scared to let my husband stay there in that prison.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to Vichy, and I couldn't do anything with Petain, because Petain immediately said he was terribly sorry, but if only I wasn't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I gave up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I returned to Saint-Etienne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then this friend of mine who was doing the card-- the identification card-- knew somebody there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he said you're going to have a hard time getting to him, because he's very suspicious.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had a whole code, and we had a-- a whole-- a whole scenery that we-- that we had mounted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went back to Vichy, and I asked an appointment with this man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had-- I had to say that I came from somebody, which I did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was finally introduced to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was very remote.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he wasn't ready to believe anything I said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
